            "text_YbjFGi": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Our Scent Scientists are the people that help harness the natural botanicals from our Cala Falco estate and craft them into sensory stories.<br/><br/><strong>Victor Alarcon - Creative Director</strong><br/>With a background in biochemistry and interdisciplinary studies, Victor Alarcón brings a research-driven and creative approach to Cala Falcó as co-founder, creative director, and head of labs. He bridges regenerative agriculture, formulation, and storytelling, leading the creation of natural, high-performance fragrances and sensory systems. Guided by a soil-to-bottle philosophy, his work uses scent to regenerate ecosystems, shape emotion, and redefine contemporary luxury.<br/><br/><strong>Tatsiana Salamanca - Lab Manager</strong><br/>With a PhD in Chemistry and nearly a decade of experience in advanced materials research, Tatsiana brings scientific precision and methodical rigor to Cala Falcó’s laboratory. She oversees the meticulous production of each formula, ensuring<br/>consistency, quality, and fidelity to the original vision.</p>",
                "width": "100%",
                "max_width": "none",
